are entitled to 10 days of paid sick leave per year.\r\nEmployees must notify their manager before the start of the workday.\r\nIf sick leave exceeds 3 consecutive days, a medical certificate is required.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 239, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6bec2dad-8677-4ea3-ad0c-528fc8e3d733": {"__data__": {"id_": "6bec2dad-8677-4ea3-ad0c-528fc8e3d733", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "C:\\Users\\ammar\\Downloads\\internship\\datasets\\Data\\LLM.txt", "file_name": "LLM.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 166, "creation_date": "2026-02-23", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-23"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "dc3ef16e-3be2-47a2-bb6f-2908656906b7", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "C:\\Users\\ammar\\Downloads\\internship\\datasets\\Data\\LLM.txt", "file_name": "LLM.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 166, "creation_date": "2026-02-23", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-23"}, "hash": "53970ffaa00ce7c2ed3d39d1e0ab3e5e6a27a9511bdfb4fbf9d5f0591bb02672", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "LLM stands for Large Language Model.\r\n\r\nExamples:\r\n- LLaMA\r\n- Gemma\r\n- GPT\r\n\r\nLLMs generate text based on prompts.\r\nThey can be combined with RAG for better accuracy.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 166, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "70388484-c7d4-4adc-85a8-773aa74a895d": {"__data__": {"id_": "70388484-c7d4-4adc-85a8-773aa74a895d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "C:\\Users\\ammar\\Downloads\\internship\\datasets\\Data\\rag.txt", "file_name": "rag.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 782, "creation_date": "2026-02-23", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-23"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "6525dce0-697e-4cfa-9d5f-176a3dc4f215", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "C:\\Users\\ammar\\Downloads\\internship\\datasets\\Data\\rag.txt", "file_name": "rag.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 782, "creation_date": "2026-02-23", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-23"}, "hash": "7ef975c9b9ab6ad8ef69adc320724cffc1bf8ac0ec63db3cfe3162faf6fb148f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "RAG stands for Retrieval-Augmented Generation.\r\n\r\nit combines a retriever and a Generator\r\n\r\nRetriever:\r\nSearches a vector database for relevant chunks.\r\n\r\nGenerator:\r\nUses retrieved context to produce grounded answers.\r\n\r\nBenefits:\r\n- Reduces hallucinations\r\n- Uses external knowledge\r\n\r\nRAG is useful when the LLM does not have access to your private or updated documents.\r\nInstead of relying on memorization, it retrieves the most relevant information from a vector database.\r\nThis improves factual accuracy and reduces hallucinations because the model answers using real retrieved context.\r\nTypical use cases include company policies, internal documentation, FAQs, and product manuals.\r\nRAG also improves transparency because you can return the source chunks used in the answer.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 782, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}}, "docstore/metadata": {"850db005-47f3-43e5-9dd9-b1e30f692495": {"doc_hash": "8636832f607e6a2f543f7edfe252d68de1720e6706de51d3527b3f1cd5e293f2", "ref_doc_id": "eca0a792-a644-4f07-b613-b0afa5d9648b"}, "e616f472-1ac6-4dbf-9cb7-272d95279604": {"doc_hash": "74368cafc7cc0dc914ad22b5a84736a7f4d3dfafe074c28912fdb1b0d76e025f", "ref_doc_id": "70270cee-1de2-4d02-85c4-9de4efbc38c3"}, "6bec2dad-8677-4ea3-ad0c-528fc8e3d733": {"doc_hash": "aa0786640f738f1053ed692dd2f20d4a6fbaa817a3857c4c7fa42cd23f68f33c", "ref_doc_id": "dc3ef16e-3be2-47a2-bb6f-2908656906b7"}, "70388484-c7d4-4adc-85a8-773aa74a895d": {"doc_hash": "fd5dfead13cfbc428c4a553012a5afeeb72d593e5f36b89d587fc99c45d64030", "ref_doc_id": "6525dce0-697e-4cfa-9d5f-176a3dc4f215"}}}